info.description:
This is a log management system for Twisted applications.
It's a way to use python logging facilities under Twisted log environment.
It contains a server to storage log messages,and a GUI to manage logging
messages browsing & logging dynamic configuration.
info.keywords: Software Development, Log Server, Twisted log
info.name: twlogging
info.summary: python logging way for twisted log
